      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7 and boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and chop your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Crush your <strong>garlic</strong> open by squashing them with the side of a knife and discard the skins</p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
