    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based <strong>hob-safe</strong> <strong>oven-proof casserole dish </strong>with a matching lid with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a high heat</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped onion</strong> and <strong>crushed garlic </strong>to the dish</p>",
